descript.abstract: This index represents the coverage of the scans of DVRPC's non-orthorectified, mylar, aerial photo enlargements for the year 1959.
descript.purpose: These polygons were developed to define the overall extent of the imagery, and to assist users in locating the particular images of interest to them.
